'''盧克·斯泰因'''（Luke Steyn，{{bd|1993年|6月7日}}）是[[辛巴威|辛巴威]]高山滑雪運動員，從2008年開始參賽。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://data.fis-ski.com/dynamic/athlete-biography.html?sector=AL&competitorid=150690 |title=Luke Steyn FIS Biography |accessdate=2016-02-07 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201183020/http://data.fis-ski.com/dynamic/athlete-biography.html?sector=AL&competitorid=150690 |dead-url=no }}</ref>斯泰因取得代表辛巴威參加[[2014年冬季奧運|2014年冬季奧運]]的參賽資格，成為首位代表辛巴威參加冬季奧運的運動員。<ref name="a">{{cite news |last= |first= |date=28 September 2013 |title=Steyn ready for Winter Olympic Games |url=http://www.herald.co.zw/steyn-ready-for-winter-olympic-games-2/ |newspaper=[[The_Herald_(Zimbabwe)|The Herald]] |location= |publisher= |accessdate=7 January 2014 |archive-date=2013-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205193052/http://www.herald.co.zw/steyn-ready-for-winter-olympic-games-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=22 August 2013 |title=Zimbabwe to send team to Winter Olympic Games |url=http://www.herald.co.zw/zimbabwe-to-send-team-to-winter-olympic-games/ |newspaper=[[The_Herald_(Zimbabwe)|The Herald]] |location= |publisher= |accessdate=7 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104211004/http://www.herald.co.zw/zimbabwe-to-send-team-to-winter-olympic-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="c">{{cite news |last= |first= |date=9 January 2014 |title=Luke Steyn qualifies for Winter Olympics |url=http://www.zbc.co.zw/news-categories/sport/40331-luke-steyn-qualifies-for-winter-olympics.html |newspaper=[[Zimbabwe_Broadcasting_Corporation|Zimbabwe Broadcasting Corporation]] |location= |publisher= |accessdate=9 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110091318/http://www.zbc.co.zw/news-categories/sport/40331-luke-steyn-qualifies-for-winter-olympics.html |archivedate=2014年1月10日 }}</ref>

斯泰因出生於辛巴威，兩歲時移居瑞士，他在那裡接觸到雪和滑雪。<ref>{{cite news |last=MacKenzie |first=Eric |date=16 January 2014 |title=Sochi Spotlight: Zimbabwe's first Winter Olympian |url=http://www.piquenewsmagazine.com/whistler/sochi-spotlight-zimbabwes-first-winter-olympian/Content?oid=2542948 |newspaper=[[Pique_Newsmagazine|Pique Newsmagazine]] |location=[[Whistler,_British_Columbia|Whistler, British Columbia]], [[Canada|Canada]] |publisher= |accessdate=16 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201144447/http://www.piquenewsmagazine.com/whistler/sochi-spotlight-zimbabwes-first-winter-olympian/Content?oid=2542948 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

